Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽管问 年轻人对爬山感兴趣真欣慰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们最近刚开始登山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她就敢说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕得都张不开嘴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这才叫普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 怎么都不知道求助别人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道就问 没什么不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是不知道求人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被老是麻烦别人的人鄙视了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 选哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是DAYPACK就有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色很好 牌子也很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要这个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1074,698)\bord0\shad0}约合￥400RMB
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打折还这么贵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好5000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够的部分我给你付
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 我要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么给我付呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“与其妥协让步 宁愿后悔也要买”
